SUMMARY:Bingo at Hillsboro Downtown Station
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nBingo every other Wednesday. Bingo is free to play! There will be 5 rounds with prizes from the Station and the Station Taphouse. The last round is a community round\, so the prizes will consist of items brought in by the you!\n\nhttps://www.hillsborodowntownstation.com/
